  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium heat",
    "add the sliced onions and cook until softened, about 8 minutes",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute",
    "add the chopped kabanos sausage and cook until browned, about 5 minutes",
    "add the cumin, coriander, and paprika, and stir to combine",
    "add the canned diced tomatoes and chicken broth, and stir to combine",
    "bring the tagine to a simmer and cook for 20 minutes",
    "season with salt to taste",
    "serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley if desired",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
